hadiths[54]{hadithnumber,text}:
2036,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab Allah Taala kisi bandey sey mohabbat karta hai to usey duniya sey isi tarah bachata hai, jis tarah tum mein sey koi aadmi apney bimar ko pani sey bachata hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- ye hadees Mehmood bin Labid key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursal tareeqe sey aai hai. 3- is bab mein Suheb aur Umme Munzir Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2037,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key sath merey ghar tashrif laye, hamarey ghar khajoor key khoshey latkey huye they, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam is mein sey khaney lagey aur aap key sath Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bhi khaney lagey , Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : Ali ! thehar jaao , thehar jaao , isliye ke abhi abhi bimari sey uthey ho, abhi kamzori baqi hai, Umme Munzir kehti hain : Ali (Raziallahu anhu) beth gaey aur Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam khatey rahey , phir mainey unkey liye chukandar aur jau tayyar ki, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney kaha : Ali ! is mein sey lo (khaao), ye tumharey mizaj key muwaafiq hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Fulaih ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- ye hadees Fulaih sey bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai jisey wo Ayub bin Abdur-Rehman sey riwayat kartey hain."
2038,"badduon ney puchha : Allah key Rasool ! kya hum (bimariyon ka ( ilaj keren? aap ney farmaya : ''haan , Allah key bando ! ilaj karo, isliye ke Allah Taala ney jo bimari paida ki hai uski dawaa bhi zarur paida ki hai, siwaye eik bimari key.'' logon ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! wo kon si bimari hai? aap ney farmaya : ''budhapa''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Masood , Abu-Hurera , abu Khuzama an Abiy, padhi. aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
2039,"jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key ghar walen bimaar hote to aap (حساء) tayyar karney ka hukm detey, (حساء) tayyar kiya jata, phir aap in ko thoda thoda peeney ka hukm detey, to wo is mein sey peetey, aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam farmatey they : ''(حساء) ghamgin key dil ko taqwiyat deta hai, aur mareez key dil sey isi tarah takleef door karta hai, jis tarah tum mein sey koi pani key zariey apney chehrey sey mail door karta hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2040,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum apney bimaron ko khaney par majbur na karo, isliye ke Allah Taala unhen khilata pilata hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
2041,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum log is kaley dane (kalonji) ko lazimi istimal karo isliye ke is mein (saam) key ilawa har bimari ki shifaa mojud hai, (saam) maut ko kehtey hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Barida , ibne-Umar aur Aaisha (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- الحبة السوداء (شونيز)  ""kalonji"" ko kehtey hain."
2042,"qabila uraina key kuchh log Madina aaye, unhen Madina ki aab aur huwa raas nahin aai , to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unhen sadqa key oonton key sath (charaagaah ki taraf) rawana kiya aur farmaya : ''tum log oontniyon key doodh aur peshab piyo.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2043,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney lohey key hathiyar sey apni jaan li , wo qiyamat key din us haal mein aayega ke uskey haath mein wo hathiyar hoga aur wo usey jahannam ki aag mein hamesha apney pet mein ghonpta rahega, aur jisney zahar kha kar khudkushi ki, to uskey haath mein wo zahar hoga, aur wo jahannam ki aag mein hamesha usey peeta rahega.''"
2044,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney lohey sey apni jaan li, uskey haath mein wo hathiyar hoga aur wo usey jahannam ki aag mein hamesha apney pet mein ghonptaa rahega, aur jisney zahar kha kar khudkushi ki, to uskey haath mein zahar hoga aur wo jahannam ki aag mein hamesha usey peeta rahega, aur jisney pahad sey gir kar khudkushi ki, wo jahannam ki aag mein hamesha girta rahega.''"
2045,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney khabees dawaa istimal karney sey mana farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : khabees dawaa sey wo dawaa murad hai jis mein zahar ho.
2046,"wo Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas hazir they jab Suwed bin Tariq ya Tariq bin Suwed ney aap sey sharab key barey mein puchha to aap ney unhen sharab sey mana farmaya, Suwed ney kaha : hum log to us sey ilaj kartey hain, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''wo dawaa nahin balke wo to khud bimari hai.''"
2047,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jis chiz sey ilaj kartey ho is mein sab sey behtar « سعوط » ( naak mein dalney wali dawaa ( , « لدود » ( munh key eik kinara sey dali janey wali dawaa ( , « حجامة » ( pachhna lagana (aur dast aawar dawaa hai, jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam bimar huye to Sahaba ney aap key munh key eik kinare mein dawaa dali , jab wo dawaa dal chukey to aap ney farmaya : ''mojud logon key bhi munh mein dawaa dalo'' ,ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain : Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) key ilawa tamam logon key munh mein dawaa dali gaee."
2048,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jis chiz sey tum ilaj kartey ho un mein sab sey behtar munh key eik kinare sey dali janey wali dawaa, naak mein dalney ki dawaa, pachhna aur dast aawar dawaa hai aur tumhara apni aakhon mein laganey ka sab sey behtar surma ismid hai, isliye ke wo beenai (nazar) ko badhata hai aur baal ugata hai.'' Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas eik surme-daani thi jis sey sotey waqt har aankh mein teen silaai lagatey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Ibaad bin Mansoor ki ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
2049,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney badan daaghney sey mana farmaya padhi. , phir bhi hum bimari mein mubtala huye to hamney badan dagh liya, lekin hum kamiyab aur kaamran nahin huye. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2050,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Asad bin Zarara key badan ko surkh phunsi ki bimari mein daaghaa. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Abi aur Jabir Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain.
2051,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam gardan ki dono janib mojud do poshida ragon aur kandhey par pachhna lagwaate they, aur aap mahine ki uneeswin satrahwi aur ikkeeswin taareekh ko pachhna lagwaate they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas aur Maaqil bin Yasar Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2052,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Meraj ki raat ka haal bayan kiya ke aap farishton ki jis jamaat key paas sey guzrey unhoney aap ko ye hukm zarur diya ke apni ummat ko pachhna lagwaaney ka hukm den. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees ibne-Masood ki riwayat sey Hasan gharib hai.
2053,"ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma key paas pachhna laganey waley teen ghulam they, un mein sey do ibne-Abbas aur unkey ehal aur ayaal key liye ghalla hasil kartey they aur eik ghulam in ko aur unkey ehal aur ayaal ko pachhna lagata tha, ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''pachhna laganey wala ghulam kya hi achchha hai, wo (faasid) khoon ko door karta hai, peeth ko halka karta hai, aur aankh ko saaf karta hai.'' aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Meraj mein farishton ki jis jamaat key paas sey guzrey unhoney ye zarur kaha ke tum pachhna zarur lagwaao, aap ney farmaya : ''tumharey pachhna lagwaaney ka sab sey behtar din mahine ki satrahwin, unniswin aur ikkeeswin taareekh hai.'' aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mazeed farmaya : ''sab sey behtar ilaj jisey tum apnaao wo naak mein dalney ki dawaa , munh key eik taraf sey dali janey wali dawaa, pachhna aur dast aawar dawaa hai.''  Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key munh mein Abbas aur Sahaba kiram ney dawaa dali, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney puchha : ''merey munh mein kis ney dawaa dali hai?'' tamam log khamosh rahey to aap ney farmaya : ''ghar mein jo bhi ho uskey munh mein dawaa dali jaey, siwaye aap key chacha Abbas key.'' Raavi Abd kehtey hain : Nazar ney kaha : (لدود) sey murad (وجور) hai (halaq mein dalney ki eik dawaa) hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Ibaad Mansoor hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain. padhi. 2- is bab mein Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2054,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko talwaar aur chaqu ya pathar aur kaantey sey jo zakham bhi lagta tha aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam mujhey is par mehndi rakhney ka zarur hukm detey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey Faaid hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- baaz logon ney is hadees ki Faaid sey riwayat kartey huye sanad mein (عن علي بن عبيد الله ، an جدته سلمى) ki bajaey (عن عبيد الله ابن علي an جدته سلمى) bayan kiya hai. (عبيد الله بن علي) hi ziyada sahih hai. (Salma) ko (Sulmaa) bhi kaha gaya hai."
2055,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney badan daaghaa ya jhaad phunk karaai wo tawakkul karney walon mein sey na raha.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Masood , ibne-Abbas aur Imran bin Husain (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2056,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney bichchhu key dank , nazare-bad aur pasli mein nikalney waley daney key silsiley mein, jhaad phunk ki ijazat di hai."
2057,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jhaad phunk sirf nazare-bad aur pasli mein nikalney waley daaney ki wajeh sey hi jayez hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Shoba ney ye hadees (عن حصين an الشعبي an بريدة an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) ki sanad sey usi key misl riwayat ki hai.
2058,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jinnon aur insan ki nazare bad sey panah manga kartey they, yahan tak ke muawwizatain (Sura Falaq aur Sura Naas) nazil huin, jab ye suraten utar gaeen to aap ney in dono ko ley liya aur inkey ilawa ko chhod diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Anas sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2059,"Asma binte Umes (Raziallahu Anha) ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! Jaafar Teyaar (Raziallahu anhu) key ladkon ko bahut jald nazare bad lag jati hai, kya main in key liye jhaad phunk karwaaun? aap ney farmaya : ''haan, isliye ke agar koi chiz taqdir par sabqat kar sakti to is par nazare-bad zarur sabqat karti.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees :(عن أيوب an عمرو بن دينار an عروة بن عامر an عبيد بن رفاعة an أسماء بنت عميس an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) ki sanad sey bhi marvi hai. 3- is bab mein Imran bin Husain aur Barida (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
2060,Allah key Rasool Hasan aur Husain Raziallahu anhuma par ye kalimaat padh kar jhaad phunk kartey they : (أعيذكما بكلمات الله التامة من كل شيطان وهامة ومن كل عين لامة) ''main tumharey liye Allah key mukammal aur purey kalimaat key waseeley sey har shetan aur halak karney waley zahreeley keedey aur nazare-bad sey panah maangta hun.'' aur aap farmatey they : ''Ismail aur Is-haq key liye isi tarah Ibrahim (Aleh.) panah maangtey they.''
2061,Unhoney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : الو (key silsiley mein logon key aetiqad) ki koi haqiqat nahin hai aur nazare-bad ka asar haqeeqi chiz hai (yani sach hai).
2062,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''agar koi chiz taqdir par sabqat ( pehal ( kar sakti to is par nazare-bad zarur sabqat ( pehal ( karti , aur jab log tum sey ghusl karaaein to tum ghusl kar lo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- Hayaa bin Habis ki riwayat (jo ooper mazkur (zikr) hai) gharib hai. 3- Sheban ney isey (عن يحيى بن أبي كثير an حية بن حابس an أبيه an أبي هريرة an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) ki sanad sey riwayat kiya hai jabke Ali bin Mubarak aur Harab bin Shaddad ney is sanad mein Abu-Hurera key waste ka zikr nahin kiya hai. 4- is bab mein Abdullah bin Amr sey bhi riwayat hai."
2063,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamen eik sariya mein bheja , hamney eik qom key paas padaao dala aur un sey ziyaafat (mehman-nawazi) ki darkhaast ki, lekin un logon ney hamari ziyaafat (mehman-nawazi) nahin ki, usi doran unkey sardar ko bichchhu ney dank maar diya, chunanche unhoney hamarey paas aa kar kaha : kya aap mein sey koi bichchhu key dank sey jhaad phunk karta hai? mainey kaha : haan , main karta hun, lekin us waqt tak nahin karunga jab tak ke tum mujhey kuchh bakriyan na dey do, unhoney kaha : hum tum ko tees bakriyan dengey, chunanche hamney qubul kar liya aur mainey saat baar Sura Fatiha padh kar is par dam kiya to wo sehat-yaab ho gaya aur hamney bakriyan ley lein, hamarey dil mein bakriyon key mutalliq kuchh khayal aaya padhi. , lihaza hamney kaha : jaldi na karo, yahan tak ke hum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas pahunch jaeyn, jab hum aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas pahunchey to mainey jo kuchh kiya tha aap sey bayan kar diya, aap ney farmaya : ''tum ney kaisey jana ke Sura Fatiha taawez (jhaad phunk ki dua) hai? tum log bakriyan ley lo aur apney sath is mein mera bhi hissey lagaao.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- Shoba , Abu Awaana Hisham aur kaee logon ney ye hadees (عن أبي المتوكل an أبي سعيد an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) ki sanad sey riwayat ki hai. 3- taaleeme Quran par muallim key liye ujrat leney ko Imam Shafai ney jayez kaha hai aur wo muallim key liye ujrat ki shart laganey ko durust samajhtey hain, unhoney isi hadees sey istidlaal kiya hai."
2064,"kuchh Sahaba (jinmein shamil main bhi tha) Arab key eik qabila key paas sey guzrey, unhoney un ki mehman nawaazi nahin ki, isi doran unka sardar bimar ho gaya, chunanche in logon ney hamarey paas aa kar kaha : aap logon key paas koi ilaj hai? hamney kaha : haan , lekin tum ney hamari mehman nawaazi nahin ki hai isliye hum us waqt tak ilaj nahin kerengey jab tak tum hamarey liye ujrat na mutayyan kar do, unhoney uski ujrat mein bakri ka eik galla muqarrar kiya, hum mein sey eik aadmi (yani mein khud) uskey ooper Sura Fatiha padh kar dam karney laga to wo sehatyaab ho gaya, phir jab hum Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye aur aap sey us waqiea ko bayan kiya to aap ney farmaya : ''tumhen kaisey malum huwa ke Sura Fatiha jhaad phunk (ki dua) hai? abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ney aap sey is par koi nakeer zikr nahin ki, aap ney farmaya : ''khaao aur apney sath is mein mera bhi hissa lagaao.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sahih hai. 2- ye hadees Aamash ki is riwayat sey jo Jaafar bin Ayas key wastey sey aai hai ziyada sahih hai. 3- kaee logon ney ye hadees :(عن أبي بشر جعفر بن أبي وحشية an أبي المتوكل an أبي سعيد) ki sanad sey riwayat ki hai."
2065,"Mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey puchha : Allah key Rasool ! jis dam sey hum jhaad phunk kartey hain, jis dawaa sey ilaj kartey hain aur jin bachaaw ki chizon sey hum apna bachaaw kartey hain (un key barey mein aap ka kya khayal hai?) kya ye Allah ki taqdir mein kuchh tabdili karti hain? aap ney farmaya : ''ye sab bhi Allah ki likhi hui taqdir hi ka hissa hain.''"
2066,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' ajwa ( khajoor ( jannat ka phal hai, is mein zahar sey shifaa mojud hai aur sehraye Arab ka «Faqaa» padhi. eik tarah ka « man » (Salwa wala « man » ( hai, uska arq aankh key liye shifaa hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- ye Muhammad bin Amr ki riwayat sey hai, hum isey sirf Muhammad bin umr hi Saeed bin Aamir ki riwayat sey jantey hain jisey wo Muhammad bin Amr sey riwayat kartey hain, padhi. 2- is bab mein Saeed bin Zaid , abu-Saeed aur Jabir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2067,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Sehraye-Arab ka Faqaa eik tarah ka « man » (Salwa wala « man » ( hai aur uska arq aankh key liye shifa hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2068,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera kehtey hain ki sahaba mein sey kuch logon ney kaha : khunbi zamin ki chechak hai, ( ye sun kar) Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' sehraye Arab ka «Faqaa» eik tarah ka « man » hai, uska arq aankh key liye shifaa hai, aur ajwa khajoor jannat key phalon mein sey eik phal hai, wo zahar key liye shifaa hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
2069,"mainey teen, paanch ya saat khumbi li, unko nichoda, phir uska arq eik shishi mein rakha aur usey eik ladki ki aankh mein dala to wo sehat yaab ho gaee."
2070,"kalonji maut key ilawa har bimari ki dawa hai. Qatada har roz kalonji key ikkis daney letey, unko eik potli mein rakh kar pani mein bhigotey phir har roz dahiney nathney mein do boond aur baaein main eik boond daltey, doosrey din baaein mein do boondein aur daahini main eik boond daltey aur teesrey roz dahiney mein do boond aur baaein main eik boond daltey ."
2071,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney kuttey ki qeemat , zaaniya aurat ki kamai aur kaahin key nazraney leney sey mana farmaya padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2072,"mein Abdullah bin Akeem abu-Maabad johni key yahan un ki iyaadat karney gaya, in ko « حمرة » ka marz tha padhi. hamney kaha : koi Taawiz waghera kyon nahin latka letey hain? unhoney kaha : maut us sey ziyada qarib hai, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney koi chiz latkaai wo usi key supurd kar diya gaya''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Abdullah bin Akeem ki hadees ko hum sirf Muhammad bin Abdur-Rehman bin abi Leila ki riwayat sey jantey hain, Abdullah bin Akeem ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey hadees nahin suni hai lekin wo aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key zamaney mein they, wo kehtey they : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hum logon key paas likh kar bheja hai."
2073,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''bukhaar jahannam ki garmi sey hota hai, lihaza usey pani sey thanda karo ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein Asma bint abu-Bakar, ibne-Umar, Zuber ki biwi, ummul-momenin Aaisha aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain (Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki riwayat aagey aa rahi hai)."
2074,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''bukhaar jahannam ki garmi sey hota hai, lihaza usey pani sey thanda karo ''."
2075,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Sahaba ko bukhar aur har qism key dard mein ye dua padhna sikhatey they, بسم الله الكبير أعوذ بالله العظيم من شر كل عرق نعار ومن شر حر النار''main badey Allah key naam sey shuru karta hun aur azmat waley Allah key wastey sey har bhadakti rag aur aag ki garmi key shar sey panah maangta hun ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- hum isey sirf Ibrahim bin Ismail bin abu-Hubeba ki riwayat sey jantey hain aur Ibrahim bin Ismail zaeeful-Hadis samjhey jatey hain, 3- baaz ahadees mein « arq Nuaar» key bajaey « arq Yuaar» bhi marvi hai."
2076,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : ''main ney irada kya ke dudh pilaney key dinon mein sohbat karney sey logon ko mana kar dun, phir mainey dekha ke Faras aur Rome key log aisa kartey hain, aur un ki aulad ko koi nuqsan nahin pahunchta''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Malik ney ye hadees عن أبي الأسود an عروة an عائشة an جدامة بنت وهب an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم ki sanad sey isi jaisi hadees riwayat ki hai, padhi. 3- is bab mein Asma bint Yazeed sey bhi riwayat hai, 4- Malik kehtey hain : « غيلہ » ye hai ke koi shakhs dudh pilaney key dinon main apni biwi sey jima kerey."
2077,"unhoney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : ''main ney irada kya tha ke dudh pilaney key dinon mein jima karney sey logon ko mana karun, phir mujhey yad aaya ke Rome aur Faras key log aisa kartey hain aur us sey un ki aulad ko koi nuqsan nahin pahunchta hai ''. Malik kehtey hain : « غيلہ » ye hai ke koi shakhs dudh pilaney key dinon main apni biwi sey jima kerey. Esa bin Ahmed kehtey hain : hum sey Is-haq bin Esa ney bayan kya wo kehtey hain : mujh sey Malik ney Abul-Aswad key wastey sey usi jaisi hadees bayan ki. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai."
2078,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Zatul-Janb  ki bimari mein zaitun ka tel aur waras padhi. tashkhis kartey they, Qatada kehtey hain is ko munh mein dala jaeyga, aur munh ki us janib sey dala jaeyga jis janib marz ho. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- abu-Adbullah ka naam Memun hai, wo eik Basra Shekh hain."
2079,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamen hukm diya ke Zatul-Janb ka ilaj qust bahri (Ud hindi) aur Zaitun key tel sey karen . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai, 2- hum isey sirf Memun ki riwayat sey jantey hain jisey wo Zaid bin Arqam sey riwayat kartey hain, 3- Memun sey kaee logon ney ye hadees riwayat ki hai."
2080,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam iyaadat key liye merey paas tashrif laye, us waqt mujhey aisa dard tha ke lagta tha wo maar daleyga, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''apney dahiney haath sey saat martaba dard ki jagah chhuo aur ye dua padho أعوذ بعزة الله وقوته وسلطانه من شر ما أجد ''main Allah ki izzat aur uski qudrat aur taqat key waseeley sey us takleef key shar sey panah maangta hun jo mujhey laahiq hai ''. mainey wesa hi kya aur Allah Taala ney meri takleef door kar di, chunanche main hamesha apney ghar walon ko aur dusron ko ye dua padhney ka mashwara deta hun . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2081,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un sey puchha ke ''daston (loose motions) key liye tum kya leti ho? ''main ney kaha : Shabram, aap ney farmaya : '' wo garm aur bahaney wala hai ''. Asma kehti hain : phir mainey « Sana» padhi. ka Mus-hil liya to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' agar kisi chiz mein maut sey shifaa hoti to « suna » mein hoti ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- is sey) yani «Sana» sey) murad dast aawar dawa hai."
2082,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas eik aadmi ney aa kar arz kya : merey bhai ko dast aa raha hai, aap ney farmaya : '' usey shehad pilao'' , chunanche usney isey pilaya , phir aaya aur arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! mainey usey shehad pilaya lekin us sey dast mein aur izafa ho gaya hai, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''usey shehad pilao'', usney usey shehad pilaya, phir aap key paas aaya aur arz kya : Allah key Rasool! mainey usey shehad pilaya lekin us sey dast mein aur izafa ho gaya hai, abu Saeed Khudri kehtey hain : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah taala (apney qol mein) sacha hai, aur tumharey bhai ka pet jhoota hai, usko shehad pilao'' , chunanche usney shehad pilaya to (is baar) achcha ho gaya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2083,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo musalman banda kisi aisey mareez ki iyaadat karey jiski maut ka abhi waqt na huwa ho aur saat baar ye dua padhey أسأل الله العظيم رب العرش العظيم أن يشفيك ''main azmat waley Allah aur azeem arsh key Malik sey dua karta hun ke wo tumhen achcha kar dey '' to zarur uski shifaa ho jati hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- hum isey sirf minhaal bin Amr ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
2084,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab tum mein sey kisi ko bukhar aaye aur bukhar aag ka eik tukda hai to wo usey pani sey bujha dey , eik behti nehar mein utrey aur pani key bahaw ki taraf apna rukh karey phir ye dua padhey : « بسم الله اللهم اشف عبدك وصدق رسولك » ''Allah key naam sey shuru karta hun, aey Allah ! apney bandey ko shifaa dey aur apney Rasool ki is baat ko sacha bana '' wo us amal ko Fajr key baad aur suraj nikalney sey pehley karey , wo us nehar mein teen din tak teen ghotey lagaey, agar teen din mein achcha na ho to paanch din tak, agar paanch din mein achcha na ho to saat din tak aur agar saat din mein achcha na ho to no din tak , Allah key hukm sey uska marz no din sey aagey nahin badheyga. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai."
2085,"Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha gaya aur main sun raha tha ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key zakham ka kis chiz sey ilaj kya gaya? unhoney kaha is chiz ko mujh sey ziyada janney wala ab koi baqi nahin hai, Ali (Raziallahu anhu) apni dhaal mein pani la rahey they, jabke Fatima (Raziallahu Anha) aap key zakham sey khoon dho rahi thin aur main aap key liye taat jala raha tha, phir usi ki raakh sey aap ka zakham bhara gaya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2086,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab mareez sehatyaab aur tandurust ho jaey to shaffafiyat aur rang mein uski misal us oley ki tarah hai jo aasman sey girta hai''.
2087,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab tum mareez key paas jaao to maut key silsiley mein uska gham door karo padhi. ye taqdir to nahin badlta hai lekin mareez ka dil khush kar deta hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai.
2088,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik aadmi ki iyadat ki jisey tapediq ka marz tha, aap ney farmaya : ''khush ho jaao isliye ke Allah Taala kehta hai : ye meri aag hai jisey main apney gunehgar bandey par musallat karta hun taake ye jahannam ki aag mein sey uska hissa bin jaey '' padhi. ."
2089,eik raat Sahaba ye ummid zahir kar rahey they ke bukhar chhotey gunahon key liye kaffara hai.
